# Project Status

Currently under active development.

The architecture is intentionally designed before adding advanced features.

---

# Roadmap

The long-term vision includes:

- Image generation
- Voice synthesis
- Video rendering
- Workflow automation
- n8n integration
- Publishing engines
- Analytics

